text: I took the plunge after reading the reviews, how can a stall has all 1 star reviews. I ordered the chilli ban mian…it’s edible and it doesn’t taste bad at all.
After the new owner took over the shop , the standard have drop by alot. Most of the food tastes are very dull.
Fish soup standard drop tremendously.  Profit focus shop. Dont waste time trying. Be careful and count your change properly.
